headline: Brad Singer to serve as Warner Bros. CFO after WBD split
summary: Singer is set to begin his new position in October in a “strategic role,” until the official formation of Warner Bros.

headline: Big Insider Buys Signal Confidence in These 2 Stocks
summary: Investors have plenty of strategies at their disposal to maximize portfolio gains, but one of the most telling approaches is keeping a close eye on insider activity. By insiders, we’re talking about the people at the very top – corporate officers, senior executives, and board members – the ones steering the ship and tasked with delivering profits for shareholders.
